righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34834,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/27\/animals-hear-adahb-qabr\/","url_meta":{"origin":5682,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Qabr: Animals hear punishment of people in the grave","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the dead are surely punished in their graves, such that even the beasts can hear their cries.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 10459 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28099,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/23\/fasting-distances-seventy-autumns\/","url_meta":{"origin":5682,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Allah delivers him from Hell by seventy autumns","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 23, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts a day in the way of Allah Almighty, by that day Allah will deliver his face from the Hellfire a distance of seventy autumns of travel.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2244 Grade: Sahih (authe